<h1 id="개발환경">개발환경</h1>
<ul>
  <li>MacBook Air (M1, 2020)</li>
  <li>OpenJDK 8</li>
  <li>Spring Tool Suite 4.14.0</li>
  <li>Spring framework 4.3.1.RELEASE</li>
